Confluent Kafka Cluster setup

1. Open [Homepage](https://confluent.cloud/home)
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)


2. Choose Default cluster
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)


Choose default cluster
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)


Choose Data Integration option
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)


Choose API Keys
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Choose global access and then choose next.
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Download the key and secrets it will be used to send data to kafka topics.
![image.png](data:image/png;base64,)
